Class TrackLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.model.TrackLibrary

  • public class TrackLibrary
extends java.lang.Object
    Library of tracks that is used when generating a custom AI grid. This class is fully annotated with JAXB for easy XML conversion.
